    <description>Customer Snapshot PoC: holds ONLY an opaque customer UUID. All customer details (PII) live in the external vault (Cloudflare D1) and are fetched live, view-only, at record-open via OA_CustomerSnapshotController — nothing is stored or synced into Salesforce. No secrets are stored here.</description>
